quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Tu sti cine Do really rebut faith
  107,2,Ala exista una mistreats orfan
  107,3,Nu advoca feeding sarac
  107,4,Si suferinta catre ala observa atingere rugaciune (Salat)
  107,5,Cine exista totally nepasator ai their rugaciune
  107,6,Ei doar arata
  107,7,Ei interzice caritate